channel.title: Withdraw 1 from bank [PI]
channel.description:
Hi I followed this guide for my pi server due the fact that there was item packet dupes everywhere. Now when I try to withdraw 1 from bank (rightclick or left click) it doesn't work. Not 100% sure if it was caused by that, cause i only just noticed it.
But, i had to follow the guide from a quote on page 2 cause it had been removed.
Guide [url=http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-server/snippets/307473-pi-fixing-all-item-packets-dupes-2.html] Fixing item packet dupes [PI][/url]
